
<p><img src="https://elroycdn.twit.tv/sites/default/files/styles/twit_album_art_144x144/public/images/shows/floss_weekly/album_art/sd/floss1400videohi.jpg?itok=gejzUDRJ" align="right" hspace="20" vspace="20" border="0" title="FLOSS Weekly (Video-HI)" alt="FLOSS Weekly (Video-HI)"/></p><p>Twine is an open-source tool for telling interactive, nonlinear stories. Chris Klimas has been creating interactive fiction since 1997, and created Twine in 2009. He also recently co-founded Unmapped Path, a studio focused on creating interactive narrative experiences for desktop and mobile.</p> 
<p><strong>Hosts:</strong> <a href="https://twit.tv/people/randal-schwartz">Randal Schwartz</a> and <a href="https://twit.tv/people/aaron-newcomb">Aaron Newcomb</a></p> 
